refactor(calendar): share event-type maps + fix imminent highlight

Addresses code review on the teacher SchoolEventsPanel.

1. isImminent no longer flags already-started events. It now requires
   the event to be strictly upcoming (start >= now) in addition to being
   within a week, so a multi-day vacances/exam that began days ago but
   hasn't ended is no longer shown with the rose "soon" highlight.

2. The TYPE_LABEL / TYPE_TONE / TYPE_SOLID / TYPE_ICON maps and the
   scope-label helper were duplicated verbatim across the parent and
   teacher dashboard panels. Extracted them into a single shared module
   (components/calendar/event-display.ts) so a new event type or palette
   change only has to be made once. Both panels now consume it; theming
   (parent blue / teacher violet) and links stay portal-specific.

